name: Inanimate Death
description:
The game consists of 4 levels

level 1 : the tutorial this level just gets you friendly with the WAS and D keys. you objective is to get to the gold pillar

Level 2: This level you have to find a specific rock and kill it, once killed it will sink into the ground allowing you to beat the level

Level 3: This level is like the last and you have to find a rock that once killed sinks into the ground

Level 4: This level is a maze and you have to go to the center to get to the golden pillar
